{"ts":"2026-07-13T08:57:24.341Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-kj4k"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-530: list --status <invalid> silently returns count 0 — validate against the status domain like --type and search status:"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"pm list --status bogusstatus returns count:0 exit 0 while pm list --type BogusType and pm search 'x' status:notarealstatus both fail fast with the valid domain. An agent reading the empty result concludes 'no matching items' — silent-wrong-data class, sibling of pm-96vo (GH-526 aggregate --sum/--avg silent 0 on unknown fields). Fix: validate --status against open|closed|canceled + configured status ids (same validator search uses) and error with the domain list; sweep other list filters (--assignee? --tag?) for the same fail-fast gap at fix time so the filter surface is uniformly validated."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","cli","gh-issue"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-13T08:57:24.341Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T08:57:24.341Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":60},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Unknown --status on list errors with the valid domain (including configured statuses); behavior consistent with search status: validator; regression tests for list/list-* variants; GH-530 closed"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-96vo","kind":"related","created_at":